modName: AOF HD TREE LoD - RealVision ENB Fix
summary: Fixes the dark tree lod when using enb.
descriptionHtml:
[color=#ff0000]I DON'T USE REALVISION ENB ANYMORE, SO YOU ARE FREE TO DO WHATEVER YOU WANT WITH MY MOD, FEEL FREE TO UPDATE IT AND UPLOAD IT WITHOUT MY PERMISSION. I MIGHT USE REALVISION ENB IN THE FUTURE, IF I DO SO, I WILL KEEP WORKING ON THIS MOD.[/color]

This little mod is an attempt to fix the dark tree lod when using ENBs such as RealVision. I made the tree lod brighter so that it looks like the rendered trees.

I have only tried it with RealVision ENB, and it works really well, so I would appreciate your comments on how it works with other ENBs. So far, It only includes the 2k version but I will upload the 4k one soon.

Check out my [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53692/?]Low Res Particles and Flora - LRPF[/url]
